 to clarify the injury list isn   t going to remove the mystery surrounding injuries  if anything  removing one of the designations may have made things less clear  with teams listing every player with a bump  scrape or bruise as questionable take the patriots  for example  gronkowski was listed as questionable in weeks   and   when he didn   t play  but also in weeks   and   when he did  guard jonathan cooper has been listed as questionable in all four games too  but has yet to play a game  defensive end trey flowers  on the other hand  was designated as questionable for the first three weeks   and played in all three games  write to andrew beaton at andrew beaton wsj com 
